content: I'm really fond of cinnamon and nutmeg, they add such a warm and cozy flavor to apple recipes. I've also been wanting to try using cardamom more, I've heard it pairs really well with apples. By the way, speaking of warm and cozy, I've been using the digital coupons at Safeway to save around $20 so far, and it's been really helpful in stocking up on some of my favorite spices and baking supplies.
